<p begin="00:02:27.350" end="00:02:31.100" style="s2"> So we have to analyze it today</p>
<p begin="00:02:31.425" end="00:02:34.525" style="s2"> I think the story of Cain and Abel is especially true</p>
<p begin="00:02:34.525" end="00:02:37.850" style="s2"> Because it not only works at the individual level</p>
<p begin="00:02:37.850" end="00:02:41.370" style="s2"> It has also been confirmed at the family and political levels</p>
