<p begin="00:06:06.500" end="00:06:10.225" style="s2"> You can try to use Freud&#39;s explanation</p>
<p begin="00:06:10.225" end="00:06:14.050" style="s2"> Freud believed that Judaism and Christianity</p>
<p begin="00:06:14.050" end="00:06:16.525" style="s2"> Is based on the following viewpoints</p>
