<p begin="00:07:23.075" end="00:07:26.825" style="s2"> However, although I think this book is full of shortcomings and errors</p>
<p begin="00:07:26.825" end="00:07:28.475" style="s2"> But the flaws are not hiding</p>
<p begin="00:07:28.500" end="00:07:31.325" style="s2"> Some books are wrong but they are valuable</p>
