<p begin="00:08:10.625" end="00:08:14.068" style="s2"> Maybe it’s to get back a comfortable feeling</p>
<p begin="00:08:14.068" end="00:08:16.350" style="s2"> This feeling is what we experienced when we were young</p>
<p begin="00:08:16.350" end="00:08:19.300" style="s2"> There is a father who seems to us to know everything</p>
