<p begin="00:09:10.275" end="00:09:12.275" style="s2"> It doesn&#39;t feel like</p>
<p begin="00:09:13.150" end="00:09:17.575" style="s2"> Something that makes you feel comfortable</p>
<p begin="00:09:17.675" end="00:09:19.403" style="s2"> When James Joyce wrote this</p>
